It’s a bold twist on the premium design, but features the expertly-crafted Chuck 70 elements you know and love.

Tên: Cold Fusion Chuck Taylor All Star Berkshire Boot High Top
Mô tả: EMBRACE THE ELEMENTS. We took inspiration from our rugged New England roots to bring you a sneaker boot that can handle it all. The Berkshire Boot combines go-to Converse comfort with the weather protection of a boot. With a water-resistant, faux leather build, a fleece lining for warmth, and the best-tested traction outsole in the game for that no-slip grip. A padded tongue and collar provides all-around comfort, together with an OrthoLite sockliner. Complete with our ionic All Star ankle patch for a cold-weather look that can handle it all.

Blending the conceptual lens of A-COLD-WALL* and game-changing Converse CX technology, the limited-edition Aeon Active CX is built for forward progress. The unique stretch bootie construction and exaggerated heel kick creates smooth ease of entry. The iconic partnership between Converse and Comme des Garçons has brought the brand’s conceptual vision to streets across the globe for over a decade—using the playful heart and eyes logo in distinct ways. This new release brings back the fan-favorite Comme des Garçons PLAY heart and eyes logo on a minimalist Chuck 70. Featured here in contrasting black on your choice of vivid blue or muted gray, the logo is instantly recognizable. It’s a bold twist on the premium design, but features the expertly-crafted Chuck 70 elements you know and love.

Tên: Comme des Garçons PLAY Chuck 70 Low Top

The two iconic brands collide on this simple, but remarkable execution – one that has become a style staple from Paris to New York.

Tên: Converse x DRKSHDW DRKSTAR Chuck 70 Low Top
Mô tả: SHATTER THE MOLD. Break from convention with the DRKSTAR Chuck 70, created by Rick Owens. The subversive design both celebrates and distorts the lines of our best-ever silhouette—literally stretching the possibilities with an elongated tongue and signature DRKSHDW toe cap. The cotton-twill upper and refined finishes add polish and couture-like sophistication to the design’s edgy look and exaggerated features. It’s the bold reinvention of a street classic. And a rebellion against the ubiquitous. Rick Owens crafts a Chuck 70 unlike any other.

Tên: DRKSHDW TURBOWPN High Top

With a rebellious mindset to challenge the ubiquitous and break convention, Rick Owens exaggerates the proportions and distorts the lines of the legendary basketball sneaker. The result is a distinct design that sits at the intersection of hoops style and subversive fashion, bringing the edge of DRKSHDW boots to an iconic ‘80s basketball high top.

The designs feel well-crafted and sophisticated while emphasizing softness through faux fur, hair-on-hide leather, terry cloth and micro suede. It’s the unique style you’d expect from CLOT. And the fuzziness you’d expect from designs inspired by pandas. Get your hands on these limited-edition panda paws while you can.

Mô tả: CONVERSE x SKY HIGH FARM WORKWEAR. Sky High Farm was founded by artist Dan Colen and came to be as part of his creative practice, evolving into the hub it is today through a process of exploration and collaboration. The 30-acre nonprofit farm has become a reliable food source for communities in need, donating 100% of its vegetables and protein. This collaborative Chuck 70 made in partnership with Sky High Farm Workwear– the brand built solely to help support the farm – uplifts the nonprofit’s commitment to expanding access to healthy, locally-grown food and investing in pathways to food sovereignty.

This limited-edition model utilizes custom details and a convergence of leather, suede and canvas to create a distinct look that could only come from Carhartt WIP.

Tên: Converse Renew One Star Remix Low Top
Mô tả: ONE WORLD. ONE STAR. Since its groundbreaking debut in 1974, the Converse One Star sneaker was later adopted and owned by the independents. Made with over 20% recycled content by weight, we updated the bold '90s edition to give it modern-day sensibility. A 100% recycled upper, lining, and laces are joined by a 10% recycled grind rubber foxing and toe cap, plus a 12% recycled outsole sourced from factory scraps. The legend lives on.

Mô tả: CONVERSE x JOSHUA VIDES. Our second collaboration with Joshua Vides is a wearable ode to artistic craftsmanship, designed to inspire fellow creators. On the Chuck 70, his signature color palette and intricate detailing tells a story of process and craft, highlighting the tools and techniques of an artist at work. From measuring tape laces to removable ankle patches, the power is in the details—unique and thoughtful touches that transform the sneaker into a visual experience of endless discovery.

In 1974, Converse launched a low-top suede version of the Chuck Taylor All Star with a simple yet impactful style change — a single star on the outside of the sneaker. A favourite of skateboarders since the '90s, and now updated for maximum durability, today's One Star Pro maintains its classic style with upgraded cushioning for impact protection. A rubber-backed, Cordura canvas upper delivers maximum durability while doubling down on the One Star's classic look.

Tên: Chuck Taylor All Star Tumbled Leather High Top

The All Star design elements you know and love keep it classic, like a diamond pattern toe bumper and rubber toe cap, while an updated tonal style walks the line between casual and luxury. Wear them your way.

Tên: Converse Jack Purcell Foundational Leather
Mô tả: Back in 1935, legendary Canadian badminton champion Jack Purcell was undefeated worldwide and increasingly frustrated with the quality of badminton footwear. In designing his own athletic shoe, Purcell created a canvas and rubber sneaker with a signature "smile" across its toe, a now-iconic celebration of personal style and casual refinement.

Tên: Chuck 70 High Top
Mô tả: The Converse All Star Chuck ’70 is our re-crafted sneaker that uses modern details to celebrate the original Chuck Taylor All Star from the 1970's. It features a slightly higher rubber foxing, a cushioned footbed that provides long-lasting comfort and a more substantial rubber toe cap. Additional vintage details include stitching on the sidewall and a heavier-grade canvas upper for comfort and durability. It’s an authentic throwback look that retains the iconic Chuck Taylor attributes you know and love, like the star-centered ankle patch and vulcanized rubber outsole.

Tên: Converse x DRKSHDW DRKSTAR Chuck 70 Low Top
Mô tả: CONVERSE x DRKSHDW. Break from convention with the DRKSTAR Chuck 70, created by Rick Owens. The subversive design both celebrates and distorts the lines of our best-ever silhouette—literally stretching the possibilities with an elongated tongue and signature DRKSHDW toe cap. The cotton-twill upper and refined finishes add polish and couture-like sophistication to the design’s edgy look and exaggerated features. It’s the bold reinvention of a street classic. And a rebellion against the ubiquitous. Rick Owens crafts a Chuck 70 unlike any other.

Tên: Chuck Taylor All Star CX High Top
Mô tả: THE INNOVATIVE CHUCK TAYLOR CX. EXTRA COMFORT. ENDLESS COOL. The Chuck Taylor has been the epitome of cool for 100 years—now, with more innovative technology, it has extra comfort and support. The Chuck Taylor CX has revolutionized with cutting-edge materials, like a re-engineered rubber for ultimate flexibility, an innovative foam phylon midsole to support your stride, and a special dynamic stretch canvas for a new, ultra-comfortable upper designed to move with you. It’s an entirely new way to wear your favorite sneaker —all day, every day.

Tên: Cold Fusion Chuck Taylor All Star Berkshire Boot High Top
Mô tả: EMBRACE THE ELEMENTS. We took inspiration from our rugged New England roots to bring you a sneaker boot that can handle it all. The Berkshire Boot combines go-to Converse comfort with the weather protection of a boot. With a water-resistant, faux leather build, a fleece lining for warmth, and the best-tested traction outsole in the game for that no-slip grip. A padded tongue and collar provides all-around comfort, together with an OrthoLite sockliner. Complete with our ionic All Star ankle patch for a cold-weather look that can handle it all.

Tên: Archive Print Run Star Hike Low Top
Mô tả: REMIX THE PAST. CREATE THE FUTURE. Designed to turn heads, this edition of the Run Star Hike is all about expressing your style. A mix of archival '80s camo and leopard prints come together on organic canvas for an unexpected look. A lightweight, molded platform and jagged outsole tread add height and traction, elevating your look – all day, every day.
